{"tid":111870,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"出黎做野一年幾，發現有正常同事已經要還神","createTime":"2017-02-07T16:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T02:21:44.000Z","uid":14756,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8b3638538499b3c3bf735f366042e0a6bc6ad8","tid":111870,"uid":14756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"一個就懶同亂到仆街，一個就蠢過豬，屌佢地老味日日係咁輪人。<br />\n<br />\n蠢個條友仲要做左幾年啦喎，乜柒都唔識仲要新人教返佢轉頭，教你都唔緊要，解釋個陣又唔聽，聽完又話唔make sense，成日瀨個system又怪又盛。都鳩嘅，個system轉過個look有幾奇呀？有冇你咁奇呀？下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做野係慢到時間停頓左咁樣，明明已經冇咩野做又呻呢呻路，聽見都想打巴佢。問埋晒啲鳩屎野都算，又返返下工做私人野，仲要大大聲驚死人唔知咁。真係唔想俾人知係同team囉屌! 日日核核突突咁撩黎撩去，都唔知佢掂過啲咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽日又要見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有正常同事要珍惜"},{"pid":"3d8194681e6ad5e0e65e5e7d24e2da868355982e","tid":111870,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:46:12.000Z","msg":"正常同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小姐您做盛行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bc37abe48f7d7bb62502ca056d4f828c0166ad","tid":111870,"uid":14756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小姐您做盛行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMarketing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你呢"},{"pid":"f665e92402998d331b37128ed26a4b771a95d7d5","tid":111870,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"可能人哋都係咁諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aad1439add16e61cac0dc13748bc9c8a018b35e","tid":111870,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:21:44.00